Specifically, the following files are adapted or taken directly from that project:

  multilib.yaml
    Structure, group/variant/mapping layout, and the explanatory comments
    are derived from the multilib.yaml.in template in the
    LLVM-embedded-toolchain-for-Arm source tree.

  picolibc-cross-files/*.txt
    The meson cross-file format and property set (skip_sanity_check,
    has_link_defsym, separate_boot_flash, etc.) follow the conventions
    established in the LLVM-embedded-toolchain-for-Arm picolibc
    cross-compilation files.

  scripts/build-compiler_rt.sh
  scripts/build-picolibc.sh
  scripts/build-libcxx.sh
    The CMake and meson invocation patterns, flag sets, and staged-install
    technique are derived from the build system of
    LLVM-embedded-toolchain-for-Arm.

The patches in patches/llvmorg-21.1.8.patch were developed independently
to enable cross-compilation for RISC-V bare-metal targets.
